commit.message:
Merge #1477

1477: Update vsce to 1.64.0 r=matklad a=kjeremy

Gets rid of the annoying warning asking you to run `npm install -g vsce` on `cargo install`.

Co-authored-by: kjeremy <kjeremy@gmail.com>
